## Product Rules

This product aims to solve the tedious and redudant task of looking up the meaning of a word on google, get real-world examples of how to use it, and adding the word to an organized list of vocabulary to help improve the user's lexical skills.
It's 2025, AI/LLMs should be used to improve the user experience as much as possible. Improving the user's experience means having a clean UI that's intuitive and straightforward.
